{"tid":2205504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國會10月二讀草案，准港人再申BNO 提案議員：no one is left behind","createTime":"2020-09-17T01:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T02:24:25.000Z","uid":364767,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f481b3d7d8bca5a255605b42ea6347dc42e566e","tid":2205504,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/DHMSMLIUU5DETKPZD2MGQZIFRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FDHMSMLIUU5DETKPZD2MGQZIFRI%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=434b0cb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FDHMSMLIUU5DETKPZD2MGQZIFRI%2F&h=d730aecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/DHMSMLIUU5DETKPZD2MGQZIFRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」生效後，英國政府隨即於7月1日宣佈修改入境規則，讓持有BNO的港人最快6年可入籍英國。英國自由民主黨國會議員卡邁克爾（Alistair Carmichael）認為有關做法，將令很多在97年後才出世的香港年輕人被遺留，故此他早前在英國國會提交草案，要求英國政府容許所有香港公民重新申請BNO，並為他們提供英國居留權，容許港人可在英國無限期居留或工作。該黨更力促英國政府確保「no one is left behind（一個不能少）」，認為現在是英國政府採取行動，與港人同行的時候（It is time to step up and stand with Hong Kong）。<br />\n<br />\n英國自由民主黨今日在該黨網站狠批「港版國安法」，指該法是中國政府鎮壓異己和立法會反對派的工具，亦成為了香港的「死亡喪鐘 （Death knell）」，將一國兩制框架下的僅餘價值徹底粉碎。該黨又指，法律監察人員和人權組織均認為「港版國安法」不只針對示威者，更會永久損害香港在一國兩制框架下所承諾的自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n對於英國政府早前宣佈着手修改入境規則，使持有BNO的港人可定居英國，自由民主黨認為做法值得歡迎，但指出由於有關措施只適用於BNO持有人及其家人，將令很多過去是香港民主運動核心、在97年以後才出世的香港年輕人被遺留。因此力促英國政府進一步保障香港人的權利和自由，不論他們現時是否持有BNO。<br />\n<br />\n該黨呼籲英國政府支持卡邁克爾提出，要求英國政府容許所有香港公民重新申請BNO，並為他們提供英國居留權的草案。有關草案將於今年10月23日在英國國會二讀。<br />\n<br />\n應該係父母有BNO，子女才可以申請補領<br />\n否則新移民實會即刻一窩蜂咁補領BNO，咁就弊囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1827cd91d621f63343b65ef0481cd5cf926b19","tid":2205504,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"14億香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241505615de3b0f5ff8acb91a4477573014a73a8","tid":2205504,"uid":255976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"禁止黑警全家申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309f93d3c76f479e6de64320e664783f2b0ec86c","tid":2205504,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a1827cd91d621f63343b65ef0481cd5cf926b19","tid":2205504,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"14億香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56b0d6da1d21d00376a211a757fc425b4cdf8c1","tid":2205504,"uid":53844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:36:13.000Z","msg":"講到好似過硬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b669d7cdadf680c4e87aa61dd514d8d5cabe368","tid":2205504,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072ae6d0eb25c76f3e715a479f3903d40b1dcee0","tid":2205504,"uid":139322,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:38:16.000Z","msg":"藍絲 多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfc66850e3387aca92e260425294300d1b6